<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>PICASso Quality Status &mdash; {{ generated_date }}</title>
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body {
    font-family: Calibri, 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
    background: #f0f0f0;
    color: #222;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .email-wrap {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 32px auto;
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 2px;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.10);
  }

  /* Top accent bar */
  .accent-bar {
    height: 5px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, {{ branding.primary_color }}, {{ branding.dark_color }});
  }

  /* Header */
  .email-header {
    padding: 24px 36px 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
  }
  .email-header .logo-line {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .se-badge {
    width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: {{ branding.dark_color }};
    color: #fff; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .company { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; color: {{ branding.dark_color }}; }

  .meta-row { font-size: 12.5px; color: #555; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .meta-row strong { color: #222; min-width: 60px; display: inline-block; }
  .subject-line {
    font-size: 17px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-top: 12px; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  /* Body */
  .email-body { padding: 24px 36px; }

  p { margin-bottom: 14px; font-size: 14px; color: #333; }

  /* Summary table */
  .summary-table {
    width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;
    margin: 18px 0 22px; font-size: 13px;
  }
  .summary-table th {
    background: {{ branding.dark_color }};
    color: #fff; padding: 8px 12px;
    text-align: left; font-size: 11.5px;
    font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  }
  .summary-table td {
    padding: 8px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
  }
  .summary-table tr:nth-child(even) td { background: #f9f9f9; }
  .summary-table tr.total-row td {
    background: #f0f8f2;
    font-weight: 700;
    border-top: 2px solid {{ branding.primary_color }};
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .num { text-align: center; font-weight: 600; }
  .num-open   { color: #C62828; }
  .num-closed { color: #2E7D32; }
  .num-total  { color: {{ branding.dark_color }}; font-size: 14px; }

  /* Highlights */
  .highlights {
    background: #FFF8E1;
    border-left: 4px solid #FFA000;
    border-radius: 0 3px 3px 0;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    margin: 0 0 20px;
  }
  .highlights-title {
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: #E65100; margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .highlights ul { padding-left: 18px; }
  .highlights li { font-size: 13px; color: #444; margin-bottom: 4px; }

  /* Critical list */
  .critical-list {
    margin: 16px 0;
  }
  .critical-list-title {
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px; color: #555; margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .critical-item {
    display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: baseline;
    padding: 6px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; font-size: 13px;
  }
  .critical-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .c-badge {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; padding: 1px 6px;
    border-radius: 3px; text-transform: uppercase;
    background: #FFEBEE; color: #B71C1C; border: 1px solid #EF9A9A;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .c-badge.high { background: #FFF3E0; color: #E65100; border-color: #FFCC80; }

  /* Footer */
  .email-footer {
    padding: 14px 36px;
    background: #fafafa;
    border-top: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
    font-size: 11.5px; color: #888;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .email-footer a { color: {{ branding.dark_color }}; text-decoration: none; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="email-wrap">

  <div class="accent-bar"></div>

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <div class="email-header">
    <div class="logo-line">
      <div class="se-badge">SE</div>
      <span class="company">Schneider Electric &mdash; PICASso</span>
    </div>
    <div class="meta-row"><strong>To:</strong> SVP / VP Leadership</div>
    <div class="meta-row"><strong>Date:</strong> {{ generated_date }}</div>
    <div class="meta-row"><strong>From:</strong> PICASso Release Management</div>
    <div class="subject-line">PICASso Project &mdash; Testing Quality Status Update</div>
  </div>

  <!-- BODY -->
  <div class="email-body">

    <p>Dear Leadership Team,</p>

    <p>
      Please find below a brief quality status update for the <strong>PICASso</strong> project,
      covering defects and bugs identified across SIT, UAT, and Production testing phases
      since <strong>January 19, 2026</strong>.
    </p>

    <!-- SUMMARY TABLE -->
    <table class="summary-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Testing Phase</th>
          <th>Issue Type</th>
          <th style="text-align:center">Reported</th>
          <th style="text-align:center">Open</th>
          <th style="text-align:center">Resolved</th>
          <th style="text-align:center">High / Critical</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {% for s in stats %}
        <tr>
          <td>{{ s.label }}</td>
          <td style="color:#666;font-size:12px">{{ s.issue_type_label }}</td>
          <td class="num num-total">{{ s.total }}</td>
          <td class="num num-open">{{ s.open }}</td>
          <td class="num num-closed">{{ s.closed }}</td>
          <td class="num" style="color:#E65100">{{ s.critical }}</td>
        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
        <tr class="total-row">
          <td colspan="2"><strong>Total</strong></td>
          <td class="num num-total">{{ total_all }}</td>
          <td class="num num-open">{{ total_open }}</td>
          <td class="num num-closed">{{ total_closed }}</td>
          <td class="num" style="color:#E65100"><strong>{{ total_critical }}</strong></td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <!-- KEY OBSERVATIONS -->
    <div class="highlights">
      <div class="highlights-title">Key Observations</div>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>{{ total_open }}</strong> issue{{ 's' if total_open != 1 else '' }} remain open
          out of <strong>{{ total_all }}</strong> total reported
          ({{ ((total_closed / total_all * 100) | round(0) | int) if total_all else 0 }}% resolution rate).
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>{{ total_critical }}</strong> High / Critical / Blocker issue{{ 's' if total_critical != 1 else '' }}
          {% if total_open > 0 %}currently require priority attention.{% else %}have all been resolved.{% endif %}
        </li>
        {% for s in stats %}
        {% if s.open > 0 %}
        <li>
          <strong>{{ s.label }}</strong>: {{ s.open }} open issue{{ 's' if s.open != 1 else '' }}
          ({{ s.closed }} resolved).
        </li>
        {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>

    {% if top_critical %}
    <!-- TOP OPEN CRITICAL ISSUES -->
    <div class="critical-list">
      <div class="critical-list-title">Open High / Critical Issues (top {{ top_critical | length }})</div>
      {% for issue in top_critical %}
      <div class="critical-item">
        <span class="c-badge {% if issue.priority | lower == 'high' %}high{% endif %}">
          {{ issue.priority }}
        </span>
        <span>{{ issue.summary }}</span>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% endif %}

    <p>
      A full detailed report is available upon request. The team is actively tracking all
      open items and working towards resolution prior to the next planned release.
    </p>

    <p>
      Please do not hesitate to reach out should you require any additional information.<br>
      <br>
      Best regards,<br>
      <strong>PICASso Release Management Team</strong>
    </p>

  </div>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <div class="email-footer">
    <span>Generated by SE-DevTools &mdash; {{ generated_date }}</span>
    <span>Schneider Electric &mdash; PICASso Project</span>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
